Name: Cresol
Classification: Pyrophoric liquids - Not classified (m-cresol)           Not applicable (o- and p-cresol)
Rationale for classification: Not pyrophoric when in contact with air at ordinary temperatures: the flashing point is 626degC for m-cresol (ICSC,1999). Classified as "solid"(o- and p-cresol), according to GHS definition

Name: Sodium decylbenzenesulfonate (C10)
Classification: Pyrophoric liquids - Not classified (liquid)
Rationale for classification: Considered non-pyrophoric when in contact with air at ordinary temperatures since the substance is used as laundry detergents (CERI-NITE Hazard Assessment, 2006), and sodium dodecylbenzenesulphonate (C12), an analog of sodium decylbenzenesulfonate, is classified as non-flammable (ICSC, 1999).

Name: Ammonium dodecylbenzenesulphonate (C12)
Classification: Pyrophoric liquids - Classification not possible (as a liquid)
Rationale for classification: No data available

Name: Carbon black

No data. (o-body)

Name: Formaldehyde
Classification: Pyrophoric liquids - Not applicable (gas), Not classified (aqueous solution)
Rationale for classification: Classified as "gas" according to GHS definition (gas). The flash point of formaldehyde (gas) is 430degC (c.c.) (ICSC (2004)), not pyrophoric when in contact with air at ordinary temperature, and its solution not pyrophoric when in contact with air at ordinary temperature.

Name: Polychlorinated terphenyls
Classification: Pyrophoric liquids - Not classified (liquid)
Rationale for classification: Considered non-pyrophoric when in contact with air at ordinary temperatures since the substance had previously been used as a fire-retardant (EHC 140 (1993). Classified into Class 9 (UN#3151 (Polyhalogenated Biphenyls (liquid; excluding polychlorinated biphenyls (UN#2315, liquid); those with concentrations of not more than 50mg/kg are not included in the Dangerous Goods list), or Polyhalogenated Terphenyls (liquid; those with concentrations of not more than 50mg/kg are not included in the Dangerous Goods list)) (UN Recommendation on the Transport of Dangerous Goods).
